London-Studioshaw-11-810x1221.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-11-800x1206.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-11-768x1157.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-11-1019x1536.jpg 1019w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-11.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-11-810x1221.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFurthering the home’s immersive natural atmosphere is a glass-enclosed outdoor shower. Nestled in the eastern courtyard, the deep sunken tub is set within a lush, almost tropical pocket of greenery – its position on the home’s east-west axis allowing for optimal morning sun. Together, the bath and shower transform daily rituals into moments of calm, rare within the city.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/a-sun-drenched-greenery-filled-home-in-the-heart-of-east-london/catching-sun-house-east-london-studioshaw-12/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-579105\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-12-810x549.jpg\" alt=\"A bedroom with a bed, potted plants, concrete walls, and large glass doors opening to an outdoor patio with lush greenery and a high window above.\" width=\"810\" height=\"549\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-12-810x549.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-12-800x542.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-12-768x520.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-12.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-12-810x549.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/a-sun-drenched-greenery-filled-home-in-the-heart-of-east-london/catching-sun-house-east-london-studioshaw-13/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-579106\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-13-810x1235.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalist outdoor shower with a rain showerhead, concrete block wall, glass panels, and several potted green plants on the floor.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1235\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-13-810x1235.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-13-800x1219.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-13-768x1171.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-13-1008x1536.jpg 1008w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-13.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-13-810x1235.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAt a systems level, Catching Sun House is a model of energy-efficient living. It integrates passive solar strategies, including orientation and thermal mass, alongside an air source heat pump and a whole-house heat recovery ventilation system. Insulation is enhanced throughout, allowing the home to stay cool in the summer and warm in the winter with minimal energy use.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/a-sun-drenched-greenery-filled-home-in-the-heart-of-east-london/catching-sun-house-east-london-studioshaw-14/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-579107\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-14-810x1186.jpg\" alt=\"A minimalist bedroom with a white bed, concrete block walls, large windows, and a view of lush green plants and trees outside.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1186\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-14-810x1186.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-14-800x1171.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-14-768x1124.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-14-1049x1536.jpg 1049w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-14.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-14-810x1186.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/a-sun-drenched-greenery-filled-home-in-the-heart-of-east-london/catching-sun-house-east-london-studioshaw-15/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-579108\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-15-810x1183.jpg\" alt=\"A bedroom with unmade white bedding next to large windows overlooks a small garden with leafy green plants and a concrete block wall.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1183\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-15-810x1183.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-15-800x1169.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-15-768x1122.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-15-1051x1536.jpg 1051w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-15.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-15-810x1183.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e“More than just a home, this project embodies a philosophy of well-being and sustainable design that is at the core of what Studioshaw stands for; daylight, greenery, and thoughtful spaces come together to create a sanctuary,” shares Shaw. “The interplay between built form and nature fosters a restorative environment, and offers a peaceful retreat from the hustle and bustle of urban life.”\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/a-sun-drenched-greenery-filled-home-in-the-heart-of-east-london/catching-sun-house-east-london-studioshaw-16/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-579109\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-16-810x536.jpg\" alt=\"A glass wall separates a lush garden with large leafy plants from a minimalist bedroom with a white bed and concrete block walls.\" width=\"810\" height=\"536\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-16-810x536.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-16-800x529.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-16-768x508.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-16.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-16-810x536.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/a-sun-drenched-greenery-filled-home-in-the-heart-of-east-london/catching-sun-house-east-london-studioshaw-17/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-579110\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-17-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A modern outdoor bathtub with metal and wood panels is set among lush green plants against a white brick wall.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-17-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-17-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-17-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-17.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-17-810x540.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/a-sun-drenched-greenery-filled-home-in-the-heart-of-east-london/catching-sun-house-east-london-studioshaw-18/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-579111\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-18-810x549.jpg\" alt=\"A modern home office with a built-in desk, red chair, bookshelf, potted cactus, and large windows letting in natural light.\" width=\"810\" height=\"549\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-18-810x549.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-18-800x542.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-18-768x520.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-18.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-18-810x549.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDespite its oasis-like aesthetic, the project involved an intricate negotiation process, including securing 27 party wall agreements. The effort was well worth it as the design is an inspiring example of how architecture can elevate well-being through a deliberate dialogue with nature.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/a-sun-drenched-greenery-filled-home-in-the-heart-of-east-london/catching-sun-house-east-london-studioshaw-19/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-579112\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-19-810x535.jpg\" alt=\"A minimalist loft room with sloped ceiling, large windows, light wood walls, a gray sofa, red chair, wall art, and a cactus near the window.\" width=\"810\" height=\"535\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-19-810x535.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-19-800x528.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-19-768x507.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-19.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-19-810x535.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/a-sun-drenched-greenery-filled-home-in-the-heart-of-east-london/catching-sun-house-east-london-studioshaw-20/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-579113\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-20-810x533.jpg\" alt=\"Contemporary house with large windows and a wooden facade set among traditional brick buildings, viewed from a rooftop with overgrown vegetation and a partial glass skylight.\" width=\"810\" height=\"533\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-20-810x533.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-20-800x527.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-20-768x506.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-20-385x252.jpg 385w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-20.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-20-810x533.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/a-sun-drenched-greenery-filled-home-in-the-heart-of-east-london/catching-sun-house-east-london-studioshaw-21/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-579114\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-21-810x537.jpg\" alt=\"Modern house with a large horizontal window on the upper floor, surrounded by trees, set among traditional brick homes under a clear blue sky.\" width=\"810\" height=\"537\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-21-810x537.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-21-800x530.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-21-768x509.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-21.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-21-810x537.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/a-sun-drenched-greenery-filled-home-in-the-heart-of-east-london/catching-sun-house-east-london-studioshaw-22/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-579115\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-22-810x514.jpg\" alt=\"Modern two-story house with large horizontal windows and wooden exterior, surrounded by trees, set among traditional brick houses at dusk.\" width=\"810\" height=\"514\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-22-810x514.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-22-800x508.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-22-768x487.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-22.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Catching-Sun-House-East-London-Studioshaw-22-810x514.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFor more information on the Catching Sun House and Studioshaw, visit \u003ca href=\"https://www.studioshaw.co.uk/projects/catching-sun-house-2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003estudioshaw.com\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003ePhotography by \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/jamesbrittainphotographs/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eJames Brittain\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n                        \n       